She picked up the fish when it was done and broke it in half. She set 
the rat on the stump and put the half of the fish infront of him.
"Enjoy my little friend."  She ate her portion of the fish and rested 
against the stump.  she watched the little fire burn down and go out.
"Well, when your done eating there, we shall continue our walk."
